<h2 class="bold font-l">Chuck Thorndyke tickles Sonic</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Thinking that Sonic is a machine, Chuck Thorndyke, Chris's grandfather, tries to dismantle him with a screwdriver. This unintentionally tickles Sonic. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AccidentalTickleTorture" class='trope-example-link'>Accidental Tickle Torture</a></p>
</div>
