<h1 id="overlay-title">Chuck Thorndyke tickles Sonic</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Thinking that Sonic is a machine, Chuck Thorndyke, Chris's grandfather, tries to dismantle him with a screwdriver. This unintentionally tickles Sonic.	</p>
